      "name": "Velocity field comparison against PIV measurements in pump volute",
      "description": "Steady-state RANS (k-omega SST) velocity predictions compared against particle image velocimetry data acquired in the pump volute at the nominal operating point (4 L/min, 2800 RPM). Normalised RMS velocity error of 8.4% in the primary flow region; elevated discrepancy (14%) near the cutwater attributed to unsteady shedding not captured by steady solver.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
