      "description": "Peak wall shear stress magnitudes and spatial distribution compared against published literature ranges for centrifugal blood pumps of comparable specific speed. CFD predictions fall within the reported range (10–350 Pa peak) for all five operating points. Qualitative agreement with published stress topology confirmed by two independent reviewers.",
