      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted on the baseline pump geometry at the design operating point (4 L/min, 2800 RPM). Coarse: 2.1M cells; medium: 6.8M cells; fine: 18.4M cells. GCI for pump head: 1.3% (medium-to-fine); GCI for volume-averaged shear rate: 4.7%. Asymptotic convergence ratio 0.98, confirming monotonic convergence. Medium mesh selected for production runs balancing accuracy and computational cost."
